{"tid":1379731,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"全部同我入黎洗腦！！提少一陣又開始分化指責！！","createTime":"2019-07-29T00:06:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-10T09:09:08.000Z","uid":42691,"like":78,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"b6ad136b76c5181a9051c31759cec93ec6eba1ac","tid":1379731,"uid":42691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T00:06:22.000Z","msg":"綜觀整場運動 <br />\n劍盾最佳狀態停留咗係立法會嗰日<br />\n<br />\n我要和勇變返最佳狀態！！！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">分化指責全部都係社運既劣根性</span></span><br />\n全部同我入黎洗腦講一次 <br />\n然後出去見到有人犯錯就講一次<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">兄弟爬山 各有各做<br />\n不分化 不指責 <br />\n不被捕 不受傷<br />\n齊上齊落 一個都不能少</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n只要兄弟同心 其利斷金<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4cf14465e010a96e8ac5f14ae7da7618e36f998","tid":1379731,"uid":42691,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T00:18:37.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">唔好擺低正皮就算<br />\n<br />\n同我入黎講一次！！！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">兄弟爬山 各有各做<br />\n不分化 不指責 <br />\n不被捕 不受傷<br />\n齊上齊落 一個都不能少</span></span>"},{"pid":"0e54adc1182b3d37e2254dcbaa5646bffb5f150e","tid":1379731,"uid":273716,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T00:19:45.000Z","msg":"不放負 不分化 不割蓆"},{"pid":"02c4c7e2b5f4c58aeb32df62a5f7dc92490750e4","tid":1379731,"uid":42691,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"0e54adc1182b3d37e2254dcbaa5646bffb5f150e","tid":1379731,"uid":273716,"like":2,"dislike":0,"sco